description:
<!--StartFragment-->

EGBE aka “Egbe The Music Boy” teams up with Prosper Menko and Asheck Blessing to come up with a song titled “confessions”. The song talks about trying times and how we should remain focused on Christ, making Him the center of our CONFESSIONS ;) . 

It is contemporary in its nature and of course , it is afrobeats at its best state. 

C**redit: Performance: EGBE featuring Prosper Menko and Asheck Blessing**

 **written by: EGBE, Wan Shey, Prosper Menko and ASheck Blessing**

 **Producer: Egbe TMB** 

**Mix and Master: D Mix**
